Chai, let’s eat.

813
00:39:00,587 --> 00:39:01,587
Hidden curves.

814
00:39:07,762 --> 00:39:09,762
How many hours did I sleep?

815
00:39:13,671 --> 00:39:16,103
Ah! All-New! Kreetha!

816
00:39:16,103 --> 00:39:17,493
This was your plan, wasn’t it?

817
00:39:17,493 --> 00:39:20,122
You staged the whole thing to lure me.

818
00:39:20,122 --> 00:39:22,268
You hired people to shoot at us, make it all dramatic.

819
00:39:22,268 --> 00:39:24,422
And then you planned to lure me here...

820
00:39:24,422 --> 00:39:26,422
to do something bad, didn’t you?

821
00:39:27,611 --> 00:39:28,611
We didn’t do anything.

822
00:39:29,722 --> 00:39:30,722
I know.

823
00:39:30,873 --> 00:39:33,383
I just wanted a scene like a drama heroine.

824
00:39:33,383 --> 00:39:34,571
You know, when she faints...

825
00:39:34,571 --> 00:39:36,071
and when she wakes up, something bad happens to her, right?

826
00:39:38,364 --> 00:39:39,364
Is it morning already?

827
00:39:41,143 --> 00:39:42,143
When did I fall asleep?

828
00:39:42,770 --> 00:39:43,770
Where did Peck and Pong go?

829
00:39:44,483 --> 00:39:45,483
Sky, do you know?

830
00:39:45,637 --> 00:39:48,221
Cycling around Bang Krachao for eco-tourism, maybe?

831
00:39:48,221 --> 00:39:49,221
How should I know?

832
00:39:49,294 --> 00:39:50,294
I passed out with you guys here.

833
00:39:51,562 --> 00:39:52,562
And they just let us go this easily?

834
00:39:53,861 --> 00:39:54,861
Isn’t that a good thing?

835
00:39:55,893 --> 00:39:57,893
But I’m still confused.

836
00:39:59,402 --> 00:40:01,402
Why was Peck shooting at you two?

837
00:40:05,391 --> 00:40:06,391
What did you do to her?

838
00:40:09,242 --> 00:40:11,667
Er...we just...

839
00:40:11,667 --> 00:40:12,667
Nothing.

840
00:40:13,297 --> 00:40:17,298
If you did nothing, why would she chase you down shooting?

841
00:40:19,895 --> 00:40:23,896
Tell me the whole truth or I’ll tell everyone.

842
00:40:26,245 --> 00:40:28,713
We were just investigating her, so she wanted to hunt us down.

843
00:40:28,713 --> 00:40:31,868
Well, why the hell were you poking into her business?

844
00:40:31,868 --> 00:40:35,777
I know you two are lying.

845
00:40:35,777 --> 00:40:39,251
Tell me properly. Who are you really?

846
00:40:39,251 --> 00:40:40,251
Tell me everything.

847
00:40:41,246 --> 00:40:42,246
And your past too.

848
00:40:45,521 --> 00:40:47,312
Tell me! Hey! Where are you going?

849
00:40:47,312 --> 00:40:49,312
You bastards! If you run I’ll make you all my husbands!

850
00:40:49,819 --> 00:40:50,819
Get back here!

851
00:40:57,090 --> 00:40:58,438
How many...er...

852
00:40:58,438 --> 00:40:59,825
How many positions did you two...

853
00:40:59,825 --> 00:41:01,825
Oh, Dad...

854
00:41:04,220 --> 00:41:05,774
may I borrow your hands?

855
00:41:05,774 --> 00:41:07,774
May I borrow your hands? It was countless.

856
00:41:08,739 --> 00:41:09,652
So what's your position?

857
00:41:09,652 --> 00:41:12,961
P.P.N. S.R.O. E.C.C. V.D.U. S.O.H.

858
00:41:12,961 --> 00:41:14,551
Is there a full name for the department?

859
00:41:14,551 --> 00:41:15,223
There is.

860
00:41:15,223 --> 00:41:15,937
What’s it called?

861
00:41:15,937 --> 00:41:20,937
P.P.V.D.U. S.S. P.P.N. H.S.R. E.C.S. H.E.C.P.N.

862
00:41:21,567 --> 00:41:22,799
I didn’t catch that. Could you say it again?

863
00:41:22,799 --> 00:41:25,660
Gosh, I don’t remember.

864
00:41:25,660 --> 00:41:26,728
I forgot already, okay?

865
00:41:26,728 --> 00:41:27,728
Got it. Must be a very big position.

866
00:42:07,809 --> 00:42:08,809
Nhon, where did my shoe go?

867
00:42:11,758 --> 00:42:12,258
It's gone now.

868
00:42:23,268 --> 00:42:24,060
Excuse me.

869
00:42:24,060 --> 00:42:25,060
Your spit...

870
00:42:30,235 --> 00:42:32,025
Dad, are you okay? Are you alright?

871
00:42:32,025 --> 00:42:33,772
Oh, it's still upright?

872
00:42:33,772 --> 00:42:35,601
Yes, it is.

873
00:42:35,601 --> 00:42:36,601
Damn it.

874
00:42:42,113 --> 00:42:44,113
The couch is ripping. There are holes now.

875
00:42:47,901 --> 00:42:49,901
Luckily, Chai's been humping till his Dad wakes up.

876
00:42:53,609 --> 00:42:54,566
Are you hurt?

877
00:42:54,766 --> 00:42:55,766
I'm alright.

878
00:42:57,479 --> 00:42:59,428
I feel such a strong connection with him.

879
00:42:59,428 --> 00:43:02,299
You’ll be named All-New.

880
00:43:02,299 --> 00:43:05,848
Worth every baht I paid for your education to make you this skilled.

881
00:43:05,848 --> 00:43:07,640
We owe him hundreds of thousands.

882
00:43:07,640 --> 00:43:09,229
If we don’t pay the interest tomorrow,

883
00:43:09,229 --> 00:43:09,907
we’re screwed.

884
00:43:09,907 --> 00:43:11,658
Where the hell am I gonna get more money?

885
00:43:11,658 --> 00:43:13,446
Could you please consider it first?

886
00:43:13,446 --> 00:43:14,795
It doesn’t really match the requirements.

887
00:43:14,795 --> 00:43:16,949
But I got the local quota, you know.

888
00:43:16,949 --> 00:43:18,544
This is about being a flight attendant, you know.

889
00:43:18,544 --> 00:43:19,732
Not enrolling in adult education.

890
00:43:19,732 --> 00:43:20,804
Why are you breaking up with me?

891
00:43:20,804 --> 00:43:22,714
Because you have no eyebrows.

892
00:43:22,714 --> 00:43:23,306
Let’s break up.

893
00:43:23,306 --> 00:43:24,216
I think we should be friends instead.

894
00:43:24,216 --> 00:43:25,716
I’ll never believe in love again.
